{
  "id": "8-2",
  "title": "Act 2: {{characters.lyra.name}}'s Code",
  "startNode": "main",
  "nodes": {
    "main": {
      "events": [
        {
          "type": "marker",
          "id": "ch8_act2_start"
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "blackout",
          "args": {
            "enabled": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "vignette",
          "args": {
            "enabled": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "fadeIn",
          "ms": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "The Priest spoke at length. About Solmaris's faith, about the purity of soul form, about the limitations and chains of the body.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 600
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "{{characters.soren.name}} listened, assessed, sought useful intelligence.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "{{characters.elias.name}} observed the cavern's structure, calculating probable exit locations.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "{{characters.alea.name}} sat silently, her face blank, her eyes moving between the Priest and the surrounding Solmaris members.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "{{characters.lyra.name}} truly listened. Because she held genuine curiosity about every form of existence, even those she could not fully endorse.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 900
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "Chief Priest",
          "text": "Among your four, there exists one soul, <delay ms=\"500\"/>of particular significance to us.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Her gaze fell upon {{characters.lyra.name}}.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 16
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.soren.name}}",
          "text": "Wait. What are you doing.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "Chief Priest",
          "text": "Simply letting her see. Letting her see her true origins.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 700
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "{{characters.lyra.name}} felt it. An external signal touched her neural interface, unfolding a data sequence at its surface, projecting it across a neural broadcast frequency all could perceive.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 600
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "It was code.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 14
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 700
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "system",
          "display": {
            "topLeft": "Soul Base Code",
            "topRight": "Deep Scan Results",
            "center": "Deepest Layer Structure: Non-Natural Newborn Soul Format\nFormat Match: Solmaris System ── <em>Perfect Match</em>",
            "bottomRight": "Implantation Time: Soul Genesis Initialization"
          },
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "instant"
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 1000
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "It was her own soul's foundational code. But in its deepest layer lay something that belonged to no natural newborn soul.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Not corruption, not implanted later, but present from the beginning—from the moment her soul first emerged in the neural network. Carefully designed, carefully buried in the deepest reaches, like a building's first foundation stone—unseen, yet supporting everything above.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 1000
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "Chief Priest",
          "text": "Seventeen years ago, Solmaris conducted an experiment. The goal was to create an individual with extreme emotional propensity, then embed her within Terminal Ark's fledgling network.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "Chief Priest",
          "text": "To observe how such extreme sensitivity would develop in the Ark's system environment, how it would influence those around her, what responses would emerge from her collision with the world.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "No one spoke.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 14
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 1000
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "Chief Priest",
          "text": "You are that experiment. <delay ms=\"600\"/>{{characters.lyra.name}}, every emotion you feel, every choice you make, everything that makes you feel like yourself—all were parameters we designed.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 1200
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "{{characters.lyra.name}} sat there, staring at the code projected in the air, as if looking at a stranger's name, yet forced to acknowledge it as her own.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 16
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 2500
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "fadeOut",
          "ms": 1500,
          "args": {
            "stay": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 600
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "vignette",
          "args": {
            "enabled": false
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "end"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  "onComplete": [
    "complete"
  ]
}